OL,3,C'An absolute joke': Mother bemoans
OL,4,Csentence of daughter's abuser
OL,6,FCaitlin Hanna's mother believes the
OL,7,Fsentence of her daughter's abuser is
OL,8,Ftoo lenient and will not deter other
OL,9,Fperpetrators.
OL,11,FThe man who manipulated, exploited and
OL,12,Fpreyed upon four "extremely
OL,13,Fvulnerable," drug addicted young
OL,14,Fwomen, including Caitlin, was handed a
OL,15,Fsix year sentence on Thursday.
