OL,3,C'An absolute joke': Mother bemoans
OL,4,Csentence of daughter's abuser
OL,6,FJailing Derek Brown at Craigavon Crown
OL,7,FCourt, Judge Donna McColgan KC imposed
OL,8,Fsentences of 58 months for the
OL,9,F"headline" offences of human
OL,10,Ftrafficking but having heard that the
OL,11,F61-year-old sexually assaulted one of
OL,12,Fthe women while she slept, the judge
OL,13,Fsaid to her mind that attack "is
OL,14,Fentirely separate."
OL,16,FAccordingly, she handed disabled Brown
OL,17,Fa further 14 months for sexually
OL,18,Fassaulting Caitlin Hanna and ordered
OL,19,Fthat it would be served consecutively.
