OL,3,C'An absolute joke': Mother bemoans
OL,4,Csentence of daughter's abuser
OL,6,FBrown, who sat in his wheelchair at
OL,7,Fthe side of the dock, his head bowed
OL,8,Fthroughout the 60 minute hearing, will
OL,9,Fspend three years behind bars and a
OL,10,Ffurther three years under supervised
OL,11,Flicence conditions. In addition, he
OL,12,Fwill also have to sign the police sex
OL,13,Foffenders register for the rest of his
OL,14,Flife.
OL,16,FCaitlin, who was trafficked, spied on
OL,17,Fand sexually assaulted by the vile
OL,18,FBrown, had only just turned 21 when
OL,19,Fshe tragically died from a suspected
OL,20,Fdrug overdose in the Brown's former
OL,21,Fhome in Lisburn in March 2022.
